# Special characters
snippet single-quote
alias ' 
    &#39;

snippet ampers-and
alias & 
    &amp;

snippet double-quote
alias " 
    &quot;

snippet greater-than
alias >> 
    &gt;

snippet less-than
alias << 
    &lt;

snippet extra_whitespace
alias <Space><Space> 
    &nbsp;

